snippet.title: IN LIGHT - Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
The journey of Yin and Yang to their destiny. A platformer art-game game developed by Sunscreen and powered by ETIC_Algarve.

Game developer: Iuri Santos & Nelson Cruz
Game Artist: Alexandre Rodrigues
Sound designer: Tomás Viegas
